### UV and UVX Installation

[How UV works](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/getting-started/)

```bash
curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh
```

### NIX Installation

[How NIX works](https://nixos.org/guides/how-nix-works/)

```bash
sh <(curl --proto '=https' --tlsv1.2 -L https://nixos.org/nix/install) --daemon
```

Enable Nix Flakes

Add the following line to `~/.config/nix/nix.conf` (create the file if it doesn't exist):

```ini
experimental-features = nix-command flakes
```

Restart Nix Daemon

```bash
sudo systemctl restart nix-daemon
```

